Job:
   Set of instructions to perform a build, test, package,image creation and deploy to Cloud Providers.

Linux:
  Core kernel features:
     Cgroups
     SELinux
     Namespace

To build Java projects:
  Maven
  Ant
  Gradle

What is Maven:
  maven is command line tool to build the java code. It is also helpful to manage the project, so it is project management 
tool.
  It also helps team to manage the project dependencies using a file called pom.xml

POM refers to Project Object Model

Maven developed by Apache Software foundation using Java.

Maven goals to build and produce the output:

  mvn clean
      compile
      test
      package
      install
      deploy
